article_title: Urgent Care Market Braces For CVS And Walgreens Entry

article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen

og.description: With the nation’s largest hospital operator HCA Holdings and the Optum unit of health insurance giant UnitedHealth Group buying and opening more urgent care centers at a rapid pace, speculation is beginning to center on whether drugstore chains will also enter the fast-growing business.
